==Spanish==

=== Noun ===
'''verde''' ''m''
# the [[colour]] [[green]]

=== Adjective ===
'''verde'''
# green in colour
# [[unripe]]
# [[inexperienced]]; [[naïve]]
# [[risqué]]
# [[unwell]]; [[sick]]

=== Usage ===
When used with the verb ''[[ser]]'' '''verde''' means literally green in colour
*Es verde - It's green
*El [[perro]] es verde - The [[dog]] is [[green]]
When used with the verb ''[[estar]]'' '''verde''' means either naïve, risqué or unwell
*¿Estás verde? - Are you unwell?
*¿Están verde los vestidos? - Are the dresses risqué?

